583
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:30,540
isn't that I hate you.

584
00:34:33,010 --> 00:34:34,010
But...

585
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:39,170
it's because you didn't like
someone wimpy like me.

586
00:34:44,640 --> 00:34:46,420
Sometimes, I wonder...

587
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:50,710
why you're so persistent in chasing me

588
00:34:51,340 --> 00:34:53,360
