597
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,910
What hurt me the most

598
00:35:24,860 --> 00:35:26,100
was the fact that the word

599
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:29,000
came out...

600
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:32,420
