If I'd known you were there,

604
00:35:45,650 --> 00:35:46,880
I wouldn't have said it.

605
00:35:48,730 --> 00:35:50,390
No, that's not it.

606
00:35:51,510 --> 00:35:54,800
I shouldn't have even said it
behind your back in the first place.

607
00:35:58,980 --> 00:35:59,980
Do you know

608
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:03,070
