609
00:36:04,730 --> 00:36:07,320
or thought you weren't good enough?

610
00:36:08,750 --> 00:36:10,720
And when I said the word "wimp",

611
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:13,780
it wasn't something I thought badly of,

612
00:36:15,170 --> 00:36:16,570
because to me,

613
00:36:17,740 --> 00:36:18,970
you...

614
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:21,090
are someone.

615
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:24,360
I want to spend the rest of my life with.

616
00:36:27,620 --> 00:36:29,230
Then why did you say it?

617
00:36:33,700 --> 00:36:34,700
Because...

618
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:37,820
I was a coward.

619
00:36:39,410 --> 00:36:40,410
Coward?

620
00:36:42,950 --> 00:36:43,950
Well...

621
00:36:44,910 --> 00:36:47,790
those friends of mine were potty-mouthed.

622
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:50,120
They always speak before they think.

623
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:54,480
And I...

624
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:56,910
didn't want to hear them

625
00:36:58,010 --> 00:36:59,790
always badmouthing about you,

626
00:37:00,620 --> 00:37:03,890
so I thought I had to get it over with.

627
00:37:07,950 --> 00:37:09,100
Though, do you know

628
00:37:10,410 --> 00:37:12,610
what I was dying to tell them?

629
00:37:22,710 --> 00:37:24,600
I wanted to tell them,

630
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,440
Yeah,

631
00:37:29,070 --> 00:37:31,010
I'm so, so into him.

632
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:35,100
I want him in my sight every day.

633
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,180
I want him next to me.

634
00:37:40,530 --> 00:37:42,100
And I never once have a second thought

635
00:37:44,730 --> 00:37:46,480
about being into him.

636
00:37:53,420 --> 00:37:55,480
And I want you to know...

637
00:37:59,390 --> 00:38:00,930
that no matter who you are,

638
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:04,400
I will always love you.

639
00:39:11,050 --> 00:39:12,530
The stars are beautiful, aren't they?

640
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:13,660
Yeah.

641
00:39:15,550 --> 00:39:16,840
Are you still cold, Moo?

642
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,800
No.

643
00:39:18,870 --> 00:39:20,070
It's cozy.

644
00:39:21,610 --> 00:39:24,020
If you feel uncomfortable,
you can tell me.

645
00:39:24,130 --> 00:39:25,060
I'll let go.

646
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:26,610
I'm not uncomfortable.

647
00:39:27,110 --> 00:39:29,140
This is kinda nice.

648
00:39:31,820 --> 00:39:32,820
At first,

649
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:34,530
I thought today

650
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:36,320
would be a bad day

651
00:39:36,350 --> 00:39:38,190
