another good day since...

654
00:39:43,350 --> 00:39:45,350
Fu! Fu!

655
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:46,660
Fu.

656
00:39:46,830 --> 00:39:47,840
I'm really sorry.

657
00:39:47,870 --> 00:39:52,040
At first, I thought it wouldn't take this long.
I didn't think there would be a sequel...

658
00:39:52,450 --> 00:39:53,450
Well,

659
00:39:54,240 --> 00:39:55,310
