No, I didn't.

666
00:40:22,170 --> 00:40:23,680
Hey, Fu! Fu!

667
00:40:24,310 --> 00:40:25,310
Do you want me to...

668
00:40:25,810 --> 00:40:28,330
I just wanted to ask
if you wanted me to leave the car with you.

669
00:40:36,350 --> 00:40:39,390
My bed.

670
00:40:45,950 --> 00:40:49,670
I'm so glad that a fluffy bed like this
exists in this world.

671
00:40:56,500 --> 00:40:58,310
I'm on cloud nine.

672
00:40:59,890 --> 00:41:01,600
It's me, Moo-Moo.

673
