676
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:24,310
Actually, you don't need to
bring it yourself.

677
00:41:24,350 --> 00:41:27,230
You can tell the staff,
or let me get it myself.

678
00:41:27,260 --> 00:41:28,690
So you can take some rest.

679
00:41:29,150 --> 00:41:31,900
I want to bring it to you myself

680
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:34,670
