Baby, I’m crush on ya.

729
00:45:04,100 --> 00:45:07,470
I need a way to flirt with you, yeah

730
00:45:07,530 --> 00:45:11,310
I have a hundred tricks
to win, win your heart.

731
00:45:11,400 --> 00:45:15,180
Add another hundred
to win, win your heart.

732
00:45:15,210 --> 00:45:17,760
Even when you're ready to leap,

733
00:45:17,780 --> 00:45:19,740
I'll always be ready to love

